Additionally, the paper discusses the use of correlation devices, which can be seen as a form of artificial intelligence, leading to the possibility of it being categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also presents general results and specialized results for congestion games, which can be seen as a form of data structures, leading to the possibility of it being categorized under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
